br />\n<br />\n另外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喺同係 喺呢到係唔係咁用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a12be30359090b8746f850664775ac2d12bf17c","tid":911237,"uid":213656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"edaea8ccc102a3bcad687129e08720c79a453f49","tid":911237,"uid":60196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3252a210f52f51da751d7d7912d84aec413c582a","tid":911237,"uid":107938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e293f9ff1b962bc30581ae39f164d696ba42bf7d","tid":911237,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T01:40:47.000Z","msg":"真係未見過人分唔到再同在"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T01:49:28.000Z","msg":"個page叫&quot;在不瘋狂就等死&quot;<br />\n你可以睇睇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T04:45:53.000Z","msg":"在同再呢啲我覺得有機會係手快打錯冇<br />\n但係&quot;嗰&quot;打做&quot;果&quot;，&quot;依家&quot;打做&quot;呢家&quot;，&quot;聽日&quot;打做&quot;天日&quot;呢堆就一撚定係不嬲打慣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T15:58:53.000Z","msg":"關於「依」同「呢」，書面正寫係「呢」。<br />\n其實所有粵語語法書係收「呢」唔用「依」，「呢」係粵語中邊嘅指示代詞「這」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EfdEbXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEfdEbXD.jpg&h=03b63129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係「呢」嘅正音係咩呢？手頭上未有字典查比你，但粵語審詞字庫同中大個資料庫就話應該係ni1（正讀）/nei1（異讀），兩者皆可。有時我哋會見到有人打字打「哩家」，我諗個「哩」應該係讀li1，中大資料庫亦都有標依個音出嚟，係因為粵語入邊聲母n/l係同音位，唔會有區別意義，所以讀li1都唔話得錯。<br />\n至於個「依」係點走出嚟？我推測係ni1嘅懶音，個鼻音發得唔到位，塞唔哂，最後變成弱化嘅半元音。啲人口頭上「依」嚟「依」去，當咗「依」係正字，最後打字都打個「依」出嚟，當埋佢係正字，簡直就係妹仔大過主人婆。"},{"pid":"ab3e9a2722bf54972d63d022d19690584b80ff29","tid":911237,"uid":135877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e293f9ff1b962bc30581ae39f164d696ba42bf7d","tid":911237,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b75913dd9d0cb181d289857c2f7b956fe08bc35","tid":911237,"uid":107938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T01:33:39.000Z","msg":"授同受我記錯，兩個係同音字。不過在同再真係好多人用錯，去一轉台灣人嘅facebook 就見到，問題係香港人都開始分唔到。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T01:40:47.000Z","msg":"真係未見過人分唔到再同在"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T17:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XQHE42J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQHE42J.jpg&h=dd02ef17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/HornyDragonTW/photos/a.205435149567218/1782275121883205/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FHornyDragonTW%2Fphotos%2Fa.205435149567218%2F1782275121883205%2F&d=K1U7%2FtP3thzROFvaaTWSMXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=03d18209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/HornyDragonTW/photos/a.205435149567218/1782275121883205/</a>"}]}